Food is good at a very reasonable price. One of the great things about this restaurant is that you can order most dishes as a half order. If you are a small group you can still try out a lot of different food. They do have an English menu as well. Just ask for it.
Good food even have half portion to choose :)
Ginseng chicken soup, must try

reviews.text: 午餐好食，但飯較小，同事表示唔夠飽要另外再叫一碗白飯

Would definitely recommend their soups.
It's nice that they have half portions so you can try more dishes at the price of one.
Food is generally tasty, service is nice. The staff helped us turn the AC higher when we asked.
An overall nice experience, would come again.

啲野好食呀，尤其係個湯，好香濃好足料，
可惜個位有啲逼，坐得唔係咁舒服
菜色的味道很合我們家的胃口哦！味道蠻正宗~還有很多小菜都可以點半分分量，這樣就可以多點幾個菜吃來嘗試一下嘍！已經來過店裡吃過好幾次
招牌雲吞雞超好食😍😍酸菜魚略嫌清淡，不過老人家都岩食。水煮魚大贊，香港好少食到咁高質嘅水煮魚，夠麻夠辣夠曬入味🤤🤤
